{"tid":1014872,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[女主播] 梁凱寧討論區6","createTime":"2019-02-09T13:56:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T13:57:37.000Z","uid":50936,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"27c70831c8f08ee18725239223cf5e32127bedfb","tid":1014872,"uid":50936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T13:56:46.000Z","msg":"34E人氣大台女主播梁凱寧討論區<br />\n<br />\n女主播梁凱寧連登相關討論區，多多指教<br />\n開始原因 : 因為都見到有好多粉絲但係連登未有討論區，所以想開個區分享及擺放cap圖，不知不覺到咗第五個post<br />\n<br />\n旨在分享梁凱寧相關資訊，歡迎分享Cap圖包括<br />\n1 當天新聞造型<br />\n2 擔任主持的新聞資訊節目<br />\n3 日常生活照update<br />\n備註：嚴禁分享其他女主播cap圖，避免混亂及離題 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官方資訊：<br />\n官方instagram(不公開帳戶)<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/maggie_leung_\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmaggie_leung_&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jI2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=c66e4e4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/maggie_leung_</a><br />\n<br />\n民間資訊：<br />\n民間Facebook fan page:<br />\n1. <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E6%A2%81%E5%87%B1%E5%AF%A7-Maggie-Leung-946954645435603/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%2587%25B1%25E5%25AF%25A7-Maggie-Leung-946954645435603%2F&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jI2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=cf026e16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E6%A2%81%E5%87%B1%E5%AF%A7-Maggie-Leung-946954645435603/</a><br />\n2. <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E6%A2%81%E5%87%B1%E5%AF%A7-Maggie-Leung-1632321630370028/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%2587%25B1%25E5%25AF%25A7-Maggie-Leung-1632321630370028%2F&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jI2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=846a9aef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E6%A2%81%E5%87%B1%E5%AF%A7-Maggie-Leung-1632321630370028/</a><br />\n<br />\n梁凱寧粉絲IG：<a href=\"https://www.inst